public abstract class AbstractBeanMetadata
extends Object
implements org.springframework.beans.factory.InitializingBean, BeanMetadata

An abstract implementation of BeanMetadata. Implementors should call the set name and propertyMetadataFactory properties prior to initializing the bean.
